comments[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-13T22:19:34.239Z",codex-root,"Duplicate check 2026-07-14: all-status searches for GH-547, suppress host rendering, exporter renderer suppression, and stdout corruption found no existing item. GitHub issue #547 is canonical external evidence; this item is deliberately left open and unclaimed."
body: "GitHub: https://github.com/unbraind/pm-cli/issues/547\n\nThis is backlog tracking only in the current immutable-history/read implementation lane. Reuse the public output contracts and avoid package-specific sentinels."
